I still can’t believe it, but Donut and I jumped our first 3* Grand Prix! Two rider mistakes led to two down, but so happy that we held our own in a difficult class! This little horse has made my dreams a reality 🍩 Thank you Donut for being the best partner I could ever ask for and for trying your heart out every time we walk in the ring! And a huge thank you to @maggie.mcalary for not laughing when I told you my goal was to jump a 3* this year, for working tirelessly to make it happen, and for believing in me, even when I had doubts. So lucky to be a part of your team!! #weLOVEdonut

Happy birthday to the best ever @maggie.mcalary!!!
There are not enough thank you’s in the world to cover all that you have done for me. You’ve made my dreams a reality and have done everything possible to help me reach my goals. There is no one else that I’d rather be on this journey with and I am so excited for what is to come!

Time for my annual post reminding you all to not be dumb and to always wear your helmet! 4 years ago today my life was forever changed by a freak accident/fall. I am so thankful that I chose to wear my helmet that day, as I firmly believe I would not be here now if I hadn’t. So grateful to @charlesowenhelmets for making the safest helmets and always striving for advancements in helmet and rider safety. Please always wear your helmet, you never know what can happen!
